dct_description_sm: Surveys of the Imperial Japanese Navy, 1932 with additions from other sources to 1937 ; U.S. Hydrographic Office Emergency Reproduction of Japanese Chart.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by contours and spot heights.
Shows coasts, low water areas, drainage, roads, buildings.
Map text in Japanese, map information in Japanese and English.
Japan Hydrographic Department seal in upper left margin.
